
Same option different for each node : define an option that changes for each node. For example, time zone '+00:00' '+01:00' '+02:00' etc
Set a given option for each node from an array (semi-colon separated list) . e.g. timezone='+00:00;+01:00;+02:00'

1. standalone sandbox, as a master
2. standalone sandbox, slave of a given replicator (--slaveof=host:hostname,thlport=portN)
3. standalone sandbox, slave of a given mysql server (--slaveof=host:hostname,user:username,password:pwd,dbport=portN)
4. Heterogenous MongoDB slave as dedicated topology (MySQL master to MongoDB slave) [DONE]
5. bristlecone load
6. Heterogenous MongoDB slave service as an add-on to existing topologies
7. Heterogenous slave services for Hadoop, Oracle, and generic applier.
